channel.title: Carnage's Evolution
channel.description:
WARNING: This page is filled with pictures. I work on this too much :o
This page is related to:
[url=http://moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,357792.0.html] Barrows development - Carnage's Evolution[/url]
When you see this sybol: [IMG]http://i588.photobucket.com/albums/ss325/Carnages_Evolution/NEW.jpg[/img] It means I've started/done it after this post was first made.
This is a [508] that I have been working on since around 26th October 2008. I'm almost finished now ^^,
Creator: Carnage Source: Massimo Server ([url=http://moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,314690.0.html]Download here[/url]) Overall Source: Palidino76 Credits: Carnage, Pali, Gravediggah (Trade), Aaron (massimo)
Features that can't be shown by pictures: Sound system, so far got the main ones (Attacking, blocking, eating ect.)
